# --- Terraform ---
**/.terraform/*
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.*
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# Terraform CLI local config (can contain creds)
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# If you ever store plan files locally
**/*.tfplan
**/*.plan

# --- Bootstrap local state (keep OUT of repo) ---
infra/bootstrap/terraform.tfstate
infra/bootstrap/terraform.tfstate.*
infra/bootstrap/.terraform/

# --- Python ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/.env
**/.env.*

# --- Build / packaging artifacts ---
**/build/
**/dist/
**/*.zip

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log

# --- IDE / OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/